Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.49,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)}Une douce neige du souvenir
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hé ! Hé, hé, hé ! Usopp !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Où es-tu, Usopp ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hé !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh ? {He isn't here}Il n'est pas là-haut ?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:13.89,0:00:15.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.51,0:00:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Où es-tu, Usopp ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hé, il t'appelle.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{O-Oh, this isn't good. Without thinking, I...}O-Oh, je ne pourrais pas me montrer maintenant.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough}Je suis sérieux ! Sors de là !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Si tu ne{} sors pas,\Nje vais te casser la gueule !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.06,0:00:35.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,On va te casser la gueule !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hé, tu sais où est Usopp, Sogeking ?\NJe ne le trouve nulle part !
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.99,0:00:45.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Ne t'inquiète pas.\N{He went back ahead of us on a small boat earlier.}Il est parti sur une petite embarcation, juste avant nous.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quoi ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pourquoi ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais ce navire lui appartient en fait maintenant.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.40,0:00:56.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just what is it they need in \Norder to recognize Usopp?}Comment diable ne reconnaissent-ils pas que c'est Usopp ?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pas ici non plus.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que se passe-t-il ?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.64,0:01:10.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As we suspected, I can't find anyone anywhere on this ship.}C'est bien ce que nous pensions.\NIl n'y a personne sur ce navire.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'est étrange.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder who on earth sailed this ship to us...}Je me demande qui a bien pu nous amener ce navire.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we definitely heard that \Nvoice calling out to us.}Mais nous avons tous entendu la même voix nous appeler.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that right?}Vous aussi ?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oui, quelqu'un nous a très certainement appelés.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.14,0:01:28.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like I said all this time... \Nit was the Merry's voice!}Comme je le disais,\Nc'était la voix du Merry !
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.40,0:01:31.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quoi ?! Vraiment ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.57,0:01:36.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N'est-ce pas, Merry ?! Dis quelque chose !
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.50,0:01:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Un navire ne {w}peut pas parler.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.80,0:01:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I kinda felt that way too, though...}J'ai un peu ressenti ça au début,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.11,0:01:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But there's no way something like that... could happen, huh?}mais quelque chose comme ça devrait être impossible, n'est-ce pas ?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.82,0:02:01.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I see a ship coming towards us!}Un navire se dirige vers nous !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Q-Quoi ?! Qui est-ce ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'est le Chapeaux de Paille !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.74,0:02:07.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ils sont vivants !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.81,0:02:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alors vous allez bien !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Galley-La Company's ship...}Un navire de la Galley-La Company ?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'est incroyable !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They rushed out in Aqua Laguna and still made it okay! I can't believe it!}Ils se sont précipités au milieu de l'Aqua Laguna\Net s'en sont sortis ! Je n'arrive pas à y croire !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ils sont revenus d'Enies Lobby !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.78,0:02:25.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Salut{!}, Ice{ pops}boss !
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stupid-burg.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quelle bande de fous.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ils ont affronté le Gouvernement Mondial...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,et {they }ont vraiment {took}tout récupéré.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Merry !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Regardez ! Leur navire{ is...} !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hé, que se passe-t-il ?!\NQu'est-ce qui s'est passé tout d'un coup ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tout d'un coup ? N'est-ce {this just}pas tout à fait naturel ?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quoi ?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It was declared that Merry could no longer sail.}Le Merry a été déclaré inapte à naviguer.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais{...} !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The }Merry{ is...} !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pops}Boss ! C'est grave ! Merry est en difficulté !\N{Please}Vous devez faire quelque chose !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.65,0:03:40.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys... This is good timing! You guys're all shipwrights, right?!}Vous arrivez à point nommé !\NVous êtes tous charpentiers de marine, n'est-ce pas ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je vous en supplie ! Faites quelque chose !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's our friend who has been traveling with us all this time!}C'est notre amie et elle a voyagé avec nous si longtemps !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Et il y a un instant, elle nous a sauvés !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alors s'il vous plaît, {pops}boss !
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then let her...}Alors permettez-lui...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{}de se reposer maintenant.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,J'ai déjà fait tout ce que je pouvais.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.57,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,C'est {this}quoi ce bruit ?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Il y a quelqu'un sur l'Île aux Débris ?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.47,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,N'est-ce {...}pas le navire du Chapeaux de Paille ?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.88,0:04:37.38,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The damage must've been caused by Aqua Laguna. It's in a terrible state.}Les dégâts de l'Aqua Laguna l'ont laissée en mauvais état.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.88,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Well, I guess it's beyond just damage...}Non, elle était comme ça avant la tempête.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.84,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Je veux prendre le large.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.06,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Qu'est-ce que c'était ?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Je veux prendre le large une dernière fois !
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.27,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Qu'est-ce que je fais ?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.51,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Il n'y a plus d'espoir pour ce navire.{..}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.18,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Iceburg-san !
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.74,0:05:36.73,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Qu'est-ce que vous faites là ?!\NUne autre grosse vague arrive !
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.62,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Merci.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.09,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Quoi ?! Tu veux prendre le large ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.05,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The sea is still stormy!}La tempête ne s'est pas encore calmée !
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.31,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,J'irai seul s'il le faut.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Quoi ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.36,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We can't let you go out there all by yourself!}Alors nous ne pouvons pas te laisser y aller tout seul !
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je {watching}suis témoin d'un miracle en ce moment{...} :
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A miracle of a ship that has long passed its limits...}Le miracle d'un navire \Nqui a depuis longtemps dépassé ses limites.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been a shipwright for many years,}En toutes mes années de charpentier de marine,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but I've never seen \Na pirate ship this incredible.}je n'ai jamais vu un navire pirate aussi remarquable.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's lived a splendid life.}Elle a vécu une vie splendide.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.97,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Let's go back, everyone!}Tout le monde, rentrons !
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.91,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Retour aux mers d'aventure !
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.15,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Merry !
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Je suis venu te chercher !
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Je comprends.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, then... are you guys ready?}Eh bien, êtes-vous prêts ?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oui.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oui.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Merry... the seabed is dark and lonesome,}Merry, le fond marin est sombre et solitaire,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so we'll watch you to the end.}alors nous t'accompagnerons jusqu'au bout.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'est peut-être { was good}mieux que Usopp {was}ne soit pas là.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Il n'y a aucun moyen... qu'il puisse supporter ça.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Des pensées ?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je ne suis pas d'accord.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.50,0:08:58.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tout le monde doit un jour dire adieu.\NC'est un adieu d'homme.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Not even a single tear should be shed.}Je ne dois pas verser une seule larme.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He, too... is prepared.}Alors lui aussi est préparé.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.15,0:09:44.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you for carrying us for \Nsuch a long time, Merry.}Tu nous as portés si longtemps.\NMerci, Merry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Neige{...} !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Une caravelle !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.63,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Yahoo !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.46,0:10:20.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Maintenant le navire pirate,\Nle Going Merry, est complet !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.39,0:10:24.80,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,À notre nouveau navire et membre d'équipage !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Look at this! \NThe Merry got damaged quite a bit!}Regardez ça !\NLe Merry a subi pas mal de dégâts !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.24,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{When navigating a sailboat, \Neveryone has to participate!}Quand on manœuvre un navire à voiles,\Ntout le monde doit faire sa part !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Learn it appropriately!}Vous devez vous en souvenir !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.00,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Oui, madame.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.37,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Je suis désolé.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.43,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{What are you doing?!}Qu'est-ce que tu fabriques ?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.52,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Entraînement au canon !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.25,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Ils ne volent {}pas très bien !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Je te dis, laisse-moi essayer !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.92,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Génial ! Tu l'as touché du premier coup !
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.64,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Waouh{...} ! Je l'ai vraiment touché du premier coup !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.39,0:11:20.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Zoro ! Hé ! C'est ma place !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{The entrance to the Grand Line \Nlies ahead of that light.}L'entrée du Grand Line\Nse trouve juste au-delà de cette lumière.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.12,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Trouver All Blue !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.96,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Devenir le roi des pirates !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.79,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Devenir le plus grand épéiste !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.90,0:11:38.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}Dessiner une carte du monde !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.00,0:11:43.26,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{In order t}D-Devenir un fier guerrier des mers !
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.66,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{We're going...}En route pour le Grand Line !{!}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.78,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,L'entrée du Grand Line est une montagne !
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.99,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Une montagne ?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.55,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Nous y sommes arrivés !
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.68,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,C'est la plus grande mer du monde !
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.41,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,{Go}Continuez !
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.50,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Nous nous envolons {}hors de là !
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.25,0:12:57.91,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Ne regardez pas en arrière !\NNous {going}continuons tout droit !
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.59,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Laissez-moi rejoindre votre équipage.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.92,0:13:11.20,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Je n'ai nulle part où aller\Net aucun endroit où me sentir chez moi.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.42,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Alors laissez-moi rester sur ce navire.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.92,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Oh, je vois.{..} Alors je suppose que nous n'avons pas le choix.{..}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.50,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,D'accord.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.48,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Luffy !
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.53,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Qui est le navigateur de ce navire ?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.20,0:13:24.49,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Nous volons !
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.49,0:13:28.68,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Génial ! Le navire vole !
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.41,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,C'est {a }Skypiea !
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je suis désolé{...} ;
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.36,0:15:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je voulais te porter encore plus loin.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je suis désolé{...} ;
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wanted to continue going on \Nadventures with you forever.}Je voulais partager des aventures avec toi pour toujours.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Merry !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Une voix{...} !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais je–
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.18,0:15:30.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's us who have to apologize, Merry!}C'est à nous de nous excuser, Merry !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.08,0:15:33.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Je ne suis pas doué pour la barre{...},
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.77,0:15:36.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so I ran you into icebergs at times...}alors je t'ai parfois fait percuter des icebergs.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There was a time I tore the sails, too.}J'ai aussi une fois déchiré tes voiles !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.27,0:15:46.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Zoro and Sanji are stupid, \Nso they broke all sorts of things!}Zoro et Sanji font les idiots ensemble,\Nalors ils ont cassé toutes sortes de choses !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp would fix them each time, \Nbut he isn't good at it!}Usopp te réparait à chaque fois,\Nmais il n'était pas très doué !
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So it's us who have to...}C'est donc à nous de nous excuser !
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mais j'ai été heureux.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much... \Nfor taking good care of me all this time.}Merci infiniment\Nd'avoir pris si bien soin de moi tout ce temps.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,J'ai vraiment été heureux...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,parce que je vous avais.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.81,0:16:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Merry !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:45.15,Credits,c,0,0,0,,Editing:\N Galaxy 9000\N\NTiming:\NPhosCity\N\NQuality Control:\Ndanpmss,\NGalaxy 9000,\NPepperjack,\NZenef\N\NSoundtracking:\N Halee\N\NGraphics:\N Datenshi\N\NKaraoke:\NKaitouYahiko\N\NTranslation:\NCrunchyroll,\NGaijin
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.88,0:10:19.02,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Every day we'd play covered in mud until the sun set}We spent every day covered in mud until the sun set
Dialogue: 5,0:10:19.12,0:10:28.22,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{It's hard to abandon those innocent days we spent}It's hard to leave behind those innocent days
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.01,0:10:38.52,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Even if I'm a dreamer, I'm still me}I'm a dreamer because that's who I am
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.67,0:10:47.14,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{So things don't all have to fit together like a jigsaw puzzle}I don't need to fit in like a piece of a jigsaw puzzle
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.76,0:10:57.04,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Just as someone's "Yes" could be a "No" to you,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.04,0:11:07.16,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{you'll surely always be free}You should always be free
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.16,0:11:17.29,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Even if tomorrow a wind passes through and breaks the puzzle}If the puzzle is missing a piece\Nwhen the wind passes through tomorrow,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.29,0:11:26.18,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{N}no one would blame you for that
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.18,0:11:31.79,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We had a dream that day}We knew we weren't wrong
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.79,0:11:36.41,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Our belief in ourselves}For the dreams we had before
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.41,0:11:45.66,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{makes us able to cross the wildly surging ocean}That helps us cross a wildly surging ocean
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.66,0:11:55.16,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We know the pain that you hold in your heart, so...}We know the pain that's in your heart,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.16,0:12:05.04,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{If you ever depart this ship and live in a different world}so even if you were to get off this ship\Nand find yourself on the other side,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.04,0:12:14.95,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{In the end, we can all surely smile}you'll surely smile in the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.25,0:13:26.95,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We continue to dream even today}We still have our dreams
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.95,0:13:37.16,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{Carrying the feelings you entrusted with us as well}And the memories given to us
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.16,0:13:46.20,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{We once again cross these rough seas and fight the pain}Today, we continue fighting the pain as we cross these rough seas
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.20,0:13:54.41,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{So that our promise won't become a lie}So that our promises won't become lies
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.41,0:14:05.37,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{And someday, to you who departed our ship and live in a different world,}And someday, to you who departed our ship to live on the other side,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.37,0:14:16.08,Lyrics,song,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}{we'll deliver the completed puzzle}we'll deliver a completed puzzle
Comment: 5,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.69,Flashbacks-720p,,0,0,0,,Whoa{...}!

